Vendored from the npm package @hashgraph/proto@2.25.0 (Hedera's published
HAPI protobuf definitions), flattened into this single directory with
path-derived names (services/basic_types.proto -> services_basic_types.proto).

Pinned to a published package version so parsing never silently drifts from
the definitions it was validated against. The block-era protos live
separately in ../proto-hapi/ (vendored from hiero-consensus-node; see
../proto-hapi/VENDOR_COMMIT).

Updates are deliberate, reviewed events: bump the package version here,
re-extract, and re-run the full test suite (snapshots, mirror differential,
signature verification).
